# DevOps Task 1 â€“ CI/CD with GitHub Actions

## Objective
Automate the build and deployment of a Node.js app using GitHub Actions and Docker.

## Steps
1. Created Node.js app
2. Dockerized the app
3. Created GitHub Actions workflow for build and push
4. Configured secrets for DockerHub authentication

## Output
Docker image auto-pushed to DockerHub on each push to main branch.
